title: Midnight to Twelve - King of Spain (2006)
description:
This is a rip of Midnight to Twelve's album King of Spain. I saw them live in concert in 2006 and this is a copy of the CD. 

"Midnight To Twelve is an explosive Rock Band out of Los Angeles, CA." -Last.fm

I ripped it in 192kbit, so that it was a little bit smaller.. the album sounds great and I hope you enjoy it.
